$pearl_page_church["contact-us"] = array ( 'content' => '[vc_row equal_height="yes" el_class="sm_mgt_0" css=".vc_custom_1507206786566{margin-top: -60px !important;}"][vc_column stretch="left" bg_pos="45% 50%" css=".vc_custom_1507207096289{margin-right: 45px !important;padding-top: 300px !important;background-image: url(http://pearl.stylemixthemes.com/church/wp-content/uploads/sites/12/2017/09/Fotolia_35298026_Subscription_Monthly_XL.jpg?id=108) !important;}" offset="vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-4"][/vc_column][vc_column offset="vc_col-lg-8 vc_col-md-8"][stm_spacer height="85" height_tablet="60" height_mobile="30"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="How PearlChurch can help" font_container="tag:h5|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" css=".vc_custom_1507207152534{margin-bottom: 32px !important;}"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1507206715465{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"]If your enquiry is about your faith, a call to ordination, organising a wedding, baptism, funeral or other service, the best first point of contact is your parish church. Many enquires can also be dealt with by your diocese in the first instance. Your Diocese is a good first point of contact and will then be able to advise you on a number of subjects or make suggestions on who best to speak to. Each diocese works autonomously and deals with the overall administration of the churches in a particular area. This includes training, mission, property and church schools.[/vc_column_text][stm_spacer height="0" height_tablet="0" height_mobile="30"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1507206421981{padding-right: 0px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="Contact your Diocese about:" font_container="tag:h5|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes" css=".vc_custom_1507207159181{margin-bottom: 32px !important;}"][vc_column_text] <ul> <li>Baptism / Marriage records</li> <li>Empty churches</li> <li>Active Churches and church owned property</li> <li>Clergy contact details</li> <li>Schools and education</li> <li>Churchwarden, PCC and Diocesan/Deanery synod queries</li> <li>Church mission and stewardship advice</li> <li>Complaint procedures</li> </ul> [/vc_column_text][stm_spacer height="0" height_tablet="0" height_mobile="30"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][stm_spacer height="85" height_tablet="60" height_mobile="30"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" el_class="sbc" css=".vc_custom_1507207418008{padding-top: 65px !important;padding-bottom: 25px !important;}"][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-3 vc_col-md-3 vc_col-xs-12"][vc_custom_heading text="Call Free" font_container="tag:h5|text_align:left|color:%23ffffff" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_column_text]<span style="color: #ffffff;">Phone: +1 376-226-3126</span> <span style="color: #ffffff;">Fax: +1 212-376-5575</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-3 vc_col-md-3 vc_col-xs-12"][vc_custom_heading text="Email us" font_container="tag:h5|text_align:left|color:%23ffffff" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_column_text]<span style="color: #ffffff;">For all other queries email us at info@pearlchurch.com or contact us via Feedback form below.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-3 vc_col-md-3 vc_col-xs-12"][vc_custom_heading text="Service Times" font_container="tag:h5|text_align:left|color:%23ffffff" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_column_text]<span style="color: #ffffff;">Sundays at 9:30am and 11:00am Worship Center. 8:15am Pastor’s Class Church Hall.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-3 vc_col-md-3 vc_col-xs-12"][vc_custom_heading text="Our Location" font_container="tag:h5|text_align:left|color:%23ffffff" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_column_text]<span style="color: #ffffff;">We are located at 1 Infinity Ave, Sacramento, CA 95014, United States.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column offset="vc